      "_id": "wrk_2908f15af772428da2bba9d68e22a0fc",
      "description": "NUST Learning Management System API for developer integrations (Moodle AJAX wrapper).\nAuthenticate with your NUST LMS credentials via `POST /auth/login` to receive a bearer token, then call any operation with `Authorization: Bearer <token>`. The NustDevKit gateway logs into the LMS on your behalf and manages the underlying session (cookie + sesskey) server-side, so you never handle the ephemeral sesskey.\n"
    },
